Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\\\"><span style=\\\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 此次培训采用“讲师讲授与互动交流”相结合的培训方式，课程涵盖产品基础课程、市场销售专项培训课程及渠道管理等相关内容，力求增强合作伙伴销售团队的整体水平。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\\\"><span style=\\\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 培训会具体安排：</span><span style=\\\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\\\"><br style=\\\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\\"/></span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\\\"><span style=\\\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\\">一、培训时间：2015年4月27日、28日，共2天。（具体安排见培训日程表）</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\\\"><span style=\\\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\\">二、培训地点：北京青竹宾馆B座5层会议中心多功能厅。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\\\"><span style=\\\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 具体地址：北京市海淀区紫竹院路车道沟1号。青竹宾馆地处青东商务区，位于海淀区西三环紫竹桥西辅路 200米路北，紧邻苏宁电器。</span></p><p><br/></p>\",\"videoIds\":[],\"type\":1,\"summary\":\"\",\"coverImageUrl\":\"https://open.fxiaoke.com/fscdn/bj/imgTxtView?imgId=A_201707_28_1a1c72997d6945fd8a8fea0dda006410.jpg\",\"isCoverImageInText\":false,\"status\":1,\"targetUrl\":\"https://www.fxiaoke.com/open/imgtext/?appId=FSAID_bec3ab9&materialId=3ec86cdd-ae2f-41f2-b67e-941abd94a7db&imageTextParamId=770d1e1e822c4532bbe5d418b27db9d8&fsEa=5411053120AF03AEEF1BF459C62D569A\",\"fileAttachments\":[]}],\"status\":1,\"keyId\":\"#M0#\"},{\"imageTextParams\":[{\"id\":\"5f4a3fb1dc5941418bbd440913eb0992\",\"title\":\"常见问题\",\"author\":\"\",\"content\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\\\">*这是给您提供的示例内容，您可以根据实际情况进行修改。</span></p><p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><br/></p><p style=\\\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\\\">1、公司多品牌解释</span></p><p style=\\\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\\\">我们公司发展多品牌战略是为了提高柜台的占有率和曝光率。智能家居现在处于行业导入期云龙混杂，如果一个品牌能做到10%的市场，那么我们6个品牌就能占有60%的市场份额，到时候我们就能制定智能家居的行业标准。</span></p><p style=\\\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\\\">2、客户咨询我公司智能家居产品报价嫌贵?</span></p><p style=\\\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\\\">智能家居产品不能只是看单价也要看总价，我们的传感器价格看上去贵，但我们是裸价，没有附加费用，整个工程下来我们价格反而便宜了。完整的产品系列确保了在行业中性价比最优。品种齐全，不用集成第三方设备，一个网关全部搞定，全程裸价。而且我们是真正意义上的物联网智能家居，和传统的智能家居相比，是有本质区别的！</span></p><p style=\\\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\\\">3、合同问题</span></p><p style=\\\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\\\">不能轻易的给客户发送合同，如果将合同发给了客户，客户有问题，让他们将问题提出来，一条条的去解决，尽量的让客户到南京来谈，让他们了解到我们公司、产品、技术等问题，认可了以后才有谈判的筹码。</span></p><p style=\\\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\\\">4、软硬件问题</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\\\">无线墙面触摸开关到底能够支持多大功率的灯？？？？四键，三键，二键各是多少？？？我有一个墙面开关AB各接5个射灯，C接3个射灯，D接一条小灯带。结果开关B键坏了，开关无作用，一通电B所控制的5只射灯就自动打开。假如说功率过大，为何A键没烧坏？</span></p><p><br/></p>\",\"videoIds\":[],\"type\":1,\"summary\":\"\",\"coverImageUrl\":\"https://open.fxiaoke.com/fscdn/bj/imgTxtView?imgId=A_201707_28_1046eaebbffa49518c3cc3c386880fbd.jpg\",\"isCoverImageInText\":false,\"status\":1,\"targetUrl\":\"https://www.fxiaoke.com/open/imgtext/?appId=FSAID_bec3ab9&materialId=e1682ee5-5311-4793-aad4-57be897ae1e8&imageTextParamId=5f4a3fb1dc5941418bbd440913eb0992&fsEa=5411053120AF03AEEF1BF459C62D569A\",\"fileAttachments\":[]}],\"status\":1,\"keyId\":\"#M1#\"},{\"imageTextParams\":[{\"id\":\"72f2effb3fde45c7ace83af535923ab6\",\"title\":\"国庆节放假时间和工作安排\",\"author\":\"\",\"content\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\\\">*这是给您提供的示例内容，您可以根据实际情况进行添加或修改。</span></p><p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot